WEBVTT

01:43.270 --> 01:45.990
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.000
[Episode 4]

01:49.110 --> 01:52.610
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

01:55.950 --> 01:56.490
Here.

01:57.270 --> 01:57.840
Eat.

01:59.210 --> 01:59.850
What's wrong?

01:59.880 --> 02:00.550
I...

02:01.140 --> 02:02.120
I'm not hungry.

02:03.190 --> 02:04.400
You haven't eaten anything all day.

02:04.430 --> 02:05.330
How can you not be hungry?

02:05.350 --> 02:05.900
Here.

02:06.150 --> 02:08.110
I...I...

02:08.949 --> 02:09.970
I'm just lying down all day

02:09.990 --> 02:11.170
without any exercise.

02:11.620 --> 02:13.290
I don't have the appetite.

02:13.630 --> 02:14.430
Don't worry.

02:14.460 --> 02:15.470
I'm really not hungry.

02:16.079 --> 02:17.750
Does it have anything to do with lying down?

02:17.950 --> 02:18.630
After you retired,

02:18.660 --> 02:19.650
you would also come home

02:19.670 --> 02:20.640
and simply lay down,

02:20.670 --> 02:21.900
just like an old turtle.

02:21.920 --> 02:22.740
You wouldn't move at all.

02:22.770 --> 02:24.700
Life is in the stillness.

02:26.260 --> 02:27.110
Just imagine.

02:27.110 --> 02:28.240
If I live over 10,000 years,

02:28.270 --> 02:29.620
an old turtle will be crawling towards you.

02:31.010 --> 02:32.500
How unserious!

02:33.690 --> 02:35.570
I'll be honest.

02:36.280 --> 02:37.180
This porridge

02:37.600 --> 02:39.180
is not as good as what you'd make.

02:39.790 --> 02:40.740
I don't like it.

02:42.150 --> 02:43.650
You should have told me earlier.

02:43.680 --> 02:45.090
I'll make you something delicious.

02:44.579 --> 02:48.150
[Bed 3]

03:05.540 --> 03:10.590
[Warm reminder: Please take care of your valuables to prevent any loss.]

03:15.750 --> 03:18.050
[Inheriting a hundred years of medical legacy, protecting the voyage of life]

03:18.100 --> 03:19.290
[Loving life gives you strength for good health]

03:18.990 --> 03:19.930
Auntie.

03:21.230 --> 03:22.530
Why are you here?

03:28.320 --> 03:29.560
Dr. Lu.

03:32.860 --> 03:34.670
C-Can I ask you a favor,

03:34.710 --> 03:35.530
please?

03:37.510 --> 03:38.680
Can you

03:39.850 --> 03:41.560
tell your director

03:43.060 --> 03:45.000
to arrange a surgery for Jiang.

03:45.690 --> 03:46.160
Auntie,

03:46.190 --> 03:47.900
this is not something I can decide.

03:48.030 --> 03:49.579
Captain Jiang, isn’t he…

03:50.710 --> 03:51.430
Yes.

03:52.160 --> 03:53.420
As you all know,

03:53.500 --> 03:54.590
Jiang

03:55.270 --> 03:56.860
had an operation before.

03:57.270 --> 03:57.600
Yes.

03:57.630 --> 03:59.030
We're aware of that.

03:59.990 --> 04:01.980
He went on a mission

04:03.150 --> 04:04.840
to catch three fugitives,

04:05.300 --> 04:07.250
and he fell from the third floor.

04:09.080 --> 04:11.130
The doctor didn't know he had sick sinus syndrome

04:11.970 --> 04:13.460
and simply sent him for the operation.

04:13.780 --> 04:15.700
They had no choice but to save him.

04:15.930 --> 04:17.610
During the operation,

04:19.470 --> 04:20.730
he bled a lot.

04:23.410 --> 04:25.270
He almost didn't wake up.

04:34.720 --> 04:36.730
I was such a loser the last time.

04:39.580 --> 04:40.950
I cried so hard I fainted a few times.

04:42.550 --> 04:44.380
I was almost sent to the ER.

04:44.890 --> 04:45.740
So,

04:47.820 --> 04:48.800
it's not that Chengyi and his father

04:48.830 --> 04:50.230
are unwilling to have the surgery.

04:53.530 --> 04:55.070
They are worried about me.

04:57.310 --> 04:58.760
They're afraid I can't handle it.

05:02.440 --> 05:04.140
But I've figured it out.

05:05.960 --> 05:07.560
I am his wife.

05:08.420 --> 05:10.130
I’m Chengyi’s mother.

05:11.370 --> 05:12.850
I should be stronger.

05:16.280 --> 05:17.140
I should...

05:18.400 --> 05:19.380
Deep down, I should strive

05:19.380 --> 05:20.800
to be the support they need.

05:20.950 --> 05:22.280
Don't you think so?

05:23.840 --> 05:24.930
So, Dr. Lu,

05:25.420 --> 05:26.520
please

05:26.980 --> 05:28.470
tell your director

05:29.670 --> 05:31.090
to arrange the surgery

05:31.110 --> 05:32.170
for Jiang.

05:32.190 --> 05:33.830
I understand how you feel.

05:33.930 --> 05:34.470
But I think

05:34.510 --> 05:35.390
we should discuss it with Captain Jiang

05:35.409 --> 05:36.820
before making a decision.

05:36.930 --> 05:37.780
Dr. Lu.

05:43.440 --> 05:44.060
Mom.

05:46.670 --> 05:48.010
I support my mom.

05:49.640 --> 05:50.870
We all hope

05:52.830 --> 05:54.560
my dad can have the surgery.

06:00.630 --> 06:01.950
Please, Dr. Lu.

06:02.710 --> 06:03.540
Auntie.

06:03.810 --> 06:05.010
Don't worry.

06:05.040 --> 06:06.230
Before the surgery,

06:06.270 --> 06:07.890
we'll assess his physical condition.

06:08.030 --> 06:09.070
We'll use medicine to lower his blood pressure

06:09.070 --> 06:10.500
into the normal range

06:10.590 --> 06:11.750
before we operate on him.

06:11.780 --> 06:13.520
We'll minimize any risk.

06:14.350 --> 06:14.930
Okay.

06:14.950 --> 06:15.380
Okay.

06:15.410 --> 06:16.020
Mom.

06:16.830 --> 06:18.120
Don't worry too much.

06:18.140 --> 06:19.580
Dr. Han mentioned that

06:19.960 --> 06:21.770
Dr. Lu is also an expert

06:21.860 --> 06:22.920
in this field.

06:23.350 --> 06:24.510
So let's not worry.

06:25.390 --> 06:26.130
Okay.

06:27.510 --> 06:28.270
Dr. Lu,

06:29.890 --> 06:31.270
I hope you can quickly

06:31.270 --> 06:32.760
shake off these negative emotions.

06:34.130 --> 06:35.400
I'll leave my dad's surgery

06:36.460 --> 06:37.450
into your good hands.

06:48.320 --> 06:48.790
Dr. Lu,

06:48.790 --> 06:50.030
can I add you as a contact on WeChat?

06:52.920 --> 06:53.590
Sure.

06:54.300 --> 06:55.240
If you have any questions,

06:55.240 --> 06:56.700
feel free to ask me.

06:57.270 --> 06:57.900
Okay.

06:59.240 --> 07:00.530
[Lu Yan]

06:59.310 --> 07:00.420
Thank you.

07:00.570 --> 07:02.270
[Request to Add Friend]

07:02.370 --> 07:02.970
[Sending]

07:03.010 --> 07:03.770
[Request to Add Friend]

07:03.870 --> 07:04.680
[Lu Yan]

07:13.430 --> 07:14.930
His blood pressure is under great control.

07:15.140 --> 07:17.050
The surgery is scheduled for tomorrow afternoon.

07:18.090 --> 07:19.480
So after midnight,

07:19.510 --> 07:20.520
he mustn't eat or drink.

07:20.610 --> 07:21.560
Tomorrow morning,

07:21.580 --> 07:22.950
we'll come and give you a drip.

07:23.030 --> 07:23.390
Okay.

07:23.390 --> 07:24.570
Rest early tonight.

07:24.720 --> 07:25.670
This is medication for his blood pressure.

07:25.870 --> 07:26.630
Tomorrow morning,

07:26.670 --> 07:27.380
take the medicine

07:27.400 --> 07:28.430
with some water.

07:28.700 --> 07:29.780
Alright. Do we have to take them all?

07:29.800 --> 07:30.300
Yes.

07:30.430 --> 07:31.180
Okay.

07:31.770 --> 07:32.770
Thank you.

07:35.460 --> 07:36.340
Why didn't you add her

07:36.900 --> 07:38.340
as a contact on WeChat?

07:39.960 --> 07:41.340
I've found the best one.

07:41.360 --> 07:42.430
No need to add anyone else.

07:43.230 --> 07:43.950
Who is it?

07:44.890 --> 07:46.150
Dr. Lu.

07:48.070 --> 07:49.250
Let me tell you.

07:49.960 --> 07:50.780
Look.

07:51.050 --> 07:53.150
I've been following her Moments.

07:54.140 --> 07:55.650
It's updated.

07:55.850 --> 07:56.340
Come.

07:56.530 --> 07:57.680
I'll reply.

07:58.170 --> 08:01.270
"Thank you."

08:01.550 --> 08:03.130
You're even sending her roses?

08:04.660 --> 08:06.610
I really like Dr. Lu.

08:06.640 --> 08:08.030
According to my observation,

08:08.630 --> 08:09.550
she is single.

08:10.590 --> 08:11.960
Not necessarily.

08:12.420 --> 08:13.030
If she

08:13.070 --> 08:14.400
doesn't post about it on Moments,

08:14.590 --> 08:15.620
how could you tell?

08:16.650 --> 08:18.530
Well, you can ask her.

08:19.160 --> 08:20.380
You're asking me to go up to her

08:20.430 --> 08:21.620
and just ask if she's single?

08:21.770 --> 08:22.890
Am I some kind of thug to you?

08:22.920 --> 08:23.960
Look at your son.

08:24.270 --> 08:25.510
I'm telling you, he's a coward.

08:25.620 --> 08:26.640
Makes you so mad, right?

08:26.670 --> 08:27.880
Your blood pressure will become high later.

08:27.910 --> 08:29.290
I've washed them.

08:29.350 --> 08:30.490
I'll head back first,

08:30.550 --> 08:31.730
and I'll bring breakfast tomorrow.

08:31.840 --> 08:32.600
Okay.

08:33.030 --> 08:34.059
You don't have to be too early tomorrow.

08:34.090 --> 08:34.990
Your dad mustn't eat.

08:35.010 --> 08:35.980
Get some more sleep.

08:36.110 --> 08:36.799
Okay.

08:37.159 --> 08:38.510
Drive safely.

08:38.549 --> 08:39.150
Okay.

08:39.780 --> 08:40.669
Sleep early.

08:40.690 --> 08:41.230
Go.

08:41.309 --> 08:42.150
Be careful.

08:42.200 --> 08:42.929
I'm off.

08:45.710 --> 08:46.940
He wouldn't be able to find a wife.

08:47.690 --> 08:49.850
He doesn't care, you know?

08:49.880 --> 08:51.540
I'm even more stressed out than he is.

09:36.710 --> 09:37.430
Mom.

09:37.500 --> 09:38.320
What's wrong?

09:38.390 --> 09:40.680
[Microphone enabled] [Speaker enabled] [Camera activated]

09:38.500 --> 09:39.590
You're at the hospital again?

09:40.000 --> 09:40.790
Working overtime again?

09:41.570 --> 09:42.010
Yes.

09:42.050 --> 09:43.040
It's later than usual tonight.

09:43.870 --> 09:44.670
Have you eaten?

09:46.350 --> 09:47.620
Yes, I have.

09:47.870 --> 09:49.070
Don't lie to me.

09:49.510 --> 09:50.960
You must really do as I say.

09:50.990 --> 09:51.980
Eat well.

09:52.030 --> 09:53.510
Otherwise, your stomach won't be good.

09:53.950 --> 09:54.960
Don't worry.

09:56.390 --> 09:57.980
Stop wandering around.

09:58.070 --> 09:59.580
It's really cold, so stay out of the wind.

09:59.670 --> 10:00.390
Don't worry.

10:00.430 --> 10:01.720
I'm feeling great!

10:02.060 --> 10:03.000
Don't worry about me.

10:03.960 --> 10:05.040
Take care of yourself.

10:05.590 --> 10:06.620
Don't worry.

10:07.110 --> 10:07.760
Bye.

10:14.590 --> 10:19.470
[Outpatient]

10:50.200 --> 10:52.070
Why are all the lights off?

11:03.790 --> 11:04.600
Are you okay?

11:07.330 --> 11:08.190
I'm fine.

11:14.580 --> 11:16.040
Why are you here?

11:17.610 --> 11:19.040
I...

11:19.570 --> 11:20.750
I happened to pass by as I have

11:20.750 --> 11:21.670
something to buy for my dad.

11:35.920 --> 11:37.720
Are you changing the light bulbs?

11:39.270 --> 11:39.880
Yes.

11:39.900 --> 11:40.910
I was just passing by.

11:40.950 --> 11:42.680
There was an aunt from

11:42.910 --> 11:43.990
the neighborhood committee who was

11:44.230 --> 11:45.030
trying to change the light bulb,

11:45.030 --> 11:46.470
but couldn't reach it.

11:46.500 --> 11:47.640
She asked me for help.

11:49.970 --> 11:51.960
The people’s police are truly different.

11:51.960 --> 11:52.350
Yes.

11:52.390 --> 11:54.010
We have to serve the people even after work.

11:54.750 --> 11:55.480
That's great.

11:55.510 --> 11:56.710
I won't be afraid to

11:56.710 --> 11:57.710
take this road in the future.

11:57.730 --> 11:58.860
There's light now.

12:00.070 --> 12:01.140
Thank you.

12:01.480 --> 12:02.850
So, this is the way you

12:02.990 --> 12:04.050
go home after work?

12:04.130 --> 12:06.160
Yes, my house is over there.

12:07.530 --> 12:08.600
As soon as I turned on the power,

12:08.630 --> 12:09.790
I saw the light come on.

12:10.570 --> 12:11.760
Thank you, young man.

12:11.790 --> 12:13.040
You've solved a big problem for us.

12:13.070 --> 12:13.930
You're welcome.

12:14.450 --> 12:15.120
Actually,

12:15.150 --> 12:16.560
we've always wanted to change the light bulb.

12:16.590 --> 12:17.880
But in this community,

12:17.910 --> 12:19.720
the workers are all elderly.

12:19.850 --> 12:20.830
I dare not let them do it.

12:20.830 --> 12:21.140
Yes.

12:21.190 --> 12:21.870
What if...

12:21.910 --> 12:22.950
they fall down, right?

12:22.950 --> 12:23.590
Yes.

12:24.350 --> 12:25.520
If you hadn't take the initiative

12:25.550 --> 12:26.560
to ask me about this,

12:26.590 --> 12:27.150
who knows when

12:27.150 --> 12:28.080
the light will finally be fixed?

12:28.120 --> 12:29.420
You're too kind.

12:29.450 --> 12:30.320
He took the initiative?

12:30.870 --> 12:31.680
Yes.

12:31.790 --> 12:32.520
He said

12:32.520 --> 12:33.880
he must change it today.

12:33.900 --> 12:34.840
He said his friend

12:34.870 --> 12:36.460
bumped into something here yesterday.

12:37.830 --> 12:38.480
Well...

12:38.510 --> 12:39.270
Auntie, look.

12:39.310 --> 12:40.490
The light is on.

12:41.110 --> 12:41.720
You...

12:41.790 --> 12:42.540
You can carry on.

12:43.080 --> 12:43.850
Alright.

12:43.900 --> 12:44.390
I'm leaving.

12:44.390 --> 12:44.630
Okay.

12:44.630 --> 12:46.010
Thank you, young man.

12:50.940 --> 12:52.020
Friend?

12:52.950 --> 12:53.870
Yes.

12:54.870 --> 12:55.920
My mom...

12:56.170 --> 12:57.890
My mom always takes this route home.

13:00.240 --> 13:01.540
Auntie?

13:01.830 --> 13:03.230
You guys...

13:03.330 --> 13:04.680
don't live here, right?

13:05.310 --> 13:06.550
You remember where I live

13:07.550 --> 13:08.940
so clearly?

13:12.900 --> 13:13.640
Well...

13:13.670 --> 13:14.520
Get back first.

13:14.770 --> 13:15.240
Okay.

13:15.270 --> 13:16.200
What about you?

13:16.590 --> 13:18.370
I-I'm going for a walk.

13:18.610 --> 13:20.570
Didn't you say you bought something for your dad?

13:20.590 --> 13:21.380
Where is it?

13:23.410 --> 13:24.400
Well...

13:24.860 --> 13:26.990
Is there a fruit shop nearby?

13:27.570 --> 13:28.280
Over there.

13:28.430 --> 13:29.280
I'll take you there.

13:29.310 --> 13:29.590
Let's go.

13:29.590 --> 13:30.320
Okay.

13:32.000 --> 13:32.590
Let's go.

13:39.430 --> 13:40.460
Take care.

13:42.990 --> 13:43.860
Dr. Lu.

13:44.870 --> 13:45.890
Is he your boyfriend?

13:46.550 --> 13:47.360
No.

13:47.390 --> 13:49.200
He is a patient's family.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.660
Go inside and pick whatever you want.

13:51.680 --> 13:52.910
There are fresh ones inside.

13:54.810 --> 13:55.870
Come in and pick.

13:54.990 --> 13:59.150
[Boutique de Fruits]

13:55.870 --> 13:56.190
Auntie.

13:56.190 --> 13:56.990
We'll pick ourselves.

13:56.990 --> 13:57.430
Okay.

14:01.910 --> 14:03.590
Uncle has to start fasting from tomorrow.

14:03.610 --> 14:04.710
Don't forget.

14:04.730 --> 14:05.680
It's on my mind.

14:06.050 --> 14:06.920
Lately, my dad's throat

14:06.990 --> 14:08.460
hurts when he eats.

14:08.480 --> 14:10.150
So I wanted to buy some fruits

14:10.170 --> 14:11.030
and make juice for him.

14:11.120 --> 14:12.830
He can drink juice,

14:13.070 --> 14:14.550
just not too sweet.

14:14.590 --> 14:16.080
Get some oranges

14:16.150 --> 14:16.670
or pears.

14:16.730 --> 14:17.350
Sure.

14:17.490 --> 14:18.240
Let me do it.

14:26.010 --> 14:27.670
It was my fault...

14:28.710 --> 14:29.600
this afternoon.

14:29.900 --> 14:31.120
I shouldn't have

14:31.750 --> 14:33.250
talked to you like that.

14:36.260 --> 14:37.070
It's okay.

14:39.710 --> 14:40.450
Lu Yan.

14:41.870 --> 14:44.130
This is not to comfort you,

14:44.810 --> 14:45.790
but I want to say,

14:46.870 --> 14:48.740
don't run away from this memory.

14:49.660 --> 14:50.870
But at the same time,

14:50.870 --> 14:52.530
don't let this memory become your burden.

14:59.360 --> 15:00.110
Boss!

15:00.130 --> 15:01.520
Can you weigh it for me?

15:01.590 --> 15:02.400
Coming.

15:02.590 --> 15:03.000
Here.

15:03.400 --> 15:04.600
Here, have some juice.

15:04.490 --> 15:08.730
[Boutique de Fruits]

15:04.760 --> 15:05.910
It's freshly squeezed.

15:05.990 --> 15:06.430
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

15:06.430 --> 15:07.280
It tastes great.

15:07.310 --> 15:08.070
Let me weigh it.

15:09.860 --> 15:11.580
How is his blood pressure?

15:11.960 --> 15:12.970
We measured it just now.

15:12.990 --> 15:14.020
It's under control.

15:14.040 --> 15:15.030
As long as it's normal.

15:15.480 --> 15:17.550
His blood pressure also can't be too low for the surgery.

15:17.900 --> 15:19.030
Don't worry.

15:20.380 --> 15:21.520
Actually...

15:22.590 --> 15:24.490
Actually, my dad wanted to have the surgery long ago.

15:26.180 --> 15:27.580
We were worried about my mom.

15:28.950 --> 15:29.950
All these years,

15:29.980 --> 15:32.010
she's been worrying about my dad and myself.

15:32.220 --> 15:33.560
It hasn't been easy for her to be

15:34.170 --> 15:35.190
constantly worrying about us.

15:39.200 --> 15:40.160
Jiang Chengyi.

15:40.840 --> 15:42.080
I promise you

15:42.270 --> 15:43.150
I will make sure Uncle

15:43.170 --> 15:44.880
makes it out safely.

15:47.260 --> 15:47.880
Okay.

15:49.210 --> 15:49.870
Here.

15:49.950 --> 15:53.360
[Boutique de Fruits]

15:50.620 --> 15:51.650
36.8 yuan.

15:51.750 --> 15:52.630
I'll just take 36 yuan.

15:52.630 --> 15:52.990
Okay.

15:53.050 --> 15:54.310
These apples just came in.

15:54.310 --> 15:55.510
It's very fresh.

15:55.540 --> 15:56.310
I'll give you two

15:56.350 --> 15:57.150
for you to try.

15:57.350 --> 15:57.980
Here.

15:59.780 --> 16:01.130
♫As the city flickers♫

16:01.540 --> 16:02.540
Young man.

16:02.480 --> 16:05.260
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

16:02.580 --> 16:04.330
Dr. Lu is very nice.

16:04.920 --> 16:06.630
My husband had kidney stones.

16:06.540 --> 16:07.830
♫And you, who love to smile♫

16:06.650 --> 16:08.280
She was the one who sent him to the hospital.

16:08.850 --> 16:11.310
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

16:09.100 --> 16:11.000
You have to trust Dr. Lu.

16:11.660 --> 16:12.390
All right.

16:12.330 --> 16:14.680
♫The humor of time♫

16:12.390 --> 16:13.110
Are you done paying?

16:13.130 --> 16:13.620
Yes.

16:13.650 --> 16:14.070
Yes?

16:14.090 --> 16:14.720
Let's go.

16:14.750 --> 16:15.510
Come again.

16:15.510 --> 16:16.080
Thank you.

16:16.130 --> 16:16.710
Auntie, we'll be going.

16:16.170 --> 16:18.610
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

16:16.710 --> 16:17.560
Lu, come often.

16:17.600 --> 16:18.310
Okay.

16:18.810 --> 16:19.780
Sorry.

16:19.680 --> 16:25.440
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

16:20.550 --> 16:21.470
What time do you

16:21.550 --> 16:22.690
get to work every morning?

16:22.870 --> 16:26.010
I have a morning meeting at 7.50 a.m.

16:26.070 --> 16:27.480
I usually reach by 7 a.m.

16:26.820 --> 16:28.440
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

16:27.500 --> 16:28.380
So early?

16:28.790 --> 16:29.730
I live here.

16:29.550 --> 16:32.410
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

16:30.340 --> 16:30.820
We've reached.

16:33.570 --> 16:34.330
Which building?

16:33.700 --> 16:35.130
♫The stubborn me♫

16:35.510 --> 16:36.520
I live right here.

16:36.360 --> 16:39.060
♫I always think of the far future♫

16:37.450 --> 16:39.150
I live by the bridge on the sixth floor.

16:39.310 --> 16:40.350
Sixth floor.

16:39.840 --> 16:41.910
♫I walk willfully♫

16:43.290 --> 16:46.210
♫Like a star revolving around♫

16:46.850 --> 16:48.160
♫I turn around♫

16:49.330 --> 16:52.820
♫But you're not behind me♫

16:49.430 --> 16:50.150
You're still

16:50.680 --> 16:52.100
riding this bicycle after so many years.

16:54.430 --> 16:55.160
Yeah.

16:54.490 --> 16:56.080
♫Losing you♫

16:55.190 --> 16:56.430
It's very sturdy.

16:56.450 --> 16:57.720
It's a shame to throw it away.

16:56.900 --> 16:59.070
♫It's so unreal♫

17:00.270 --> 17:01.690
♫I hurt my love♫

17:02.410 --> 17:03.350
♫But still hope to♫

17:03.550 --> 17:05.150
I thought you'd forgotten about it.

17:04.099 --> 17:06.800
♫Start anew♫

17:06.030 --> 17:07.150
How could I forget?

17:07.980 --> 17:10.010
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

17:10.950 --> 17:13.089
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

17:14.640 --> 17:16.609
♫When you're not here♫

17:16.829 --> 17:18.230
Is this for me?

17:17.410 --> 17:20.720
♫Life becomes aimless♫

17:18.829 --> 17:19.470
That's right.

17:19.550 --> 17:20.829
If I can't give you a ride in the future,

17:20.869 --> 17:22.079
you'll have to ride it yourself.

17:21.579 --> 17:23.260
♫I miss you♫

17:22.349 --> 17:23.670
Go slow and be careful.

17:23.710 --> 17:24.740
Don't worry.

17:24.329 --> 17:26.480
♫It's so real♫

17:25.069 --> 17:26.180
From now on,

17:26.230 --> 17:27.510
you'll be ferrying me.

17:27.579 --> 17:29.120
♫The person I trust♫

17:28.790 --> 17:31.430
Hello, Buddy Jiang.

17:29.700 --> 17:30.800
♫Insists on separating♫

17:31.310 --> 17:34.240
♫Who can explain?♫

17:32.590 --> 17:34.190
So then, Buddy Lu,

17:34.310 --> 17:35.340
aren't you going to say anything?

17:35.470 --> 17:37.390
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

17:38.440 --> 17:40.650
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

17:41.480 --> 17:43.910
♫To feel my heartache♫

17:44.890 --> 17:46.460
♫When I no longer have the best♫

17:46.080 --> 17:49.540
[Discounts available from 50% off]

17:47.510 --> 17:51.230
♫I miss you missing me♫

17:54.990 --> 17:56.080
What took you so long?

17:58.190 --> 17:59.240
Sorry.

17:59.260 --> 18:00.270
What do you want to eat?

18:00.290 --> 18:01.320
I want to eat

18:01.470 --> 18:02.310
spicy hot pot.

18:02.380 --> 18:03.140
Spicy hot pot.

18:03.160 --> 18:04.070
Spicy hot pot again?

18:03.230 --> 18:04.410
♫When I walk the path you've walked♫

18:04.160 --> 18:05.070
I want to eat spicy hot pot.

18:05.070 --> 18:05.790
If you eat spicy hot pot every day,

18:05.200 --> 18:08.150
♫Waiting to bump into you on the street♫

18:05.790 --> 18:06.680
you'll become spicy hot pot one day,

18:06.680 --> 18:06.990
you know?

18:06.990 --> 18:07.850
If I turn into spicy hot pot,

18:08.210 --> 18:09.510
then so be it.

18:09.650 --> 18:11.140
♫Like yesterday♫

18:09.870 --> 18:10.350
You'd better turn me

18:10.350 --> 18:11.060
into spicy hot pot instead.

18:11.060 --> 18:12.140
You want to become spicy hot pot too?

18:12.040 --> 18:14.580
♫Our forever had no end♫

18:12.230 --> 18:12.790
Sure.

18:13.760 --> 18:14.830
Did you miss me?

18:14.920 --> 18:15.590
I missed you.

18:15.840 --> 18:16.810
♫I'm the stupid one♫

18:18.960 --> 18:19.790
How much did you miss me?

18:19.720 --> 18:22.120
♫You've been engraved into my pulse♫

18:19.790 --> 18:20.990
How much? How much?

18:21.010 --> 18:21.710
How much?

18:22.440 --> 18:23.830
I missed you so much, it's like I've lost my way home.

18:23.560 --> 18:29.060
♫I don't want you to disappear like a rainbow♫

18:24.510 --> 18:25.750
Let me show you the way.

18:25.830 --> 18:26.270
Let's go.

18:29.750 --> 18:30.230
Go!

18:30.820 --> 18:31.990
♫Losing you♫

18:33.110 --> 18:35.180
♫It's so unreal♫

18:36.530 --> 18:37.690
♫I hurt my love♫

18:38.220 --> 18:39.320
♫But still hope to♫

18:39.890 --> 18:42.830
♫Start anew♫

18:44.110 --> 18:46.050
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

18:44.660 --> 18:45.620
Jiang Chengyi.

18:45.710 --> 18:47.490
Why did you drink so much?

18:46.970 --> 18:49.060
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

18:47.910 --> 18:48.810
I can't walk.

18:48.870 --> 18:49.870
I can't walk anymore.

18:49.870 --> 18:51.070
You drank so much at the gathering.

18:50.860 --> 18:52.780
♫Losing you♫

18:51.110 --> 18:51.750
It's ridiculous.

18:51.750 --> 18:52.230
Let's sit down.

18:52.250 --> 18:53.140
Okay, we'll sit.

18:53.470 --> 18:56.700
♫Life becomes aimless♫

18:54.670 --> 18:55.510
Are you feeling awful?

18:55.550 --> 18:56.150
Yes.

18:56.390 --> 18:57.590
Look at you.

18:57.860 --> 18:59.220
♫My love♫

18:59.990 --> 19:01.710
Why did you drink so much?

19:00.490 --> 19:02.580
♫Must be honest♫

19:01.750 --> 19:02.750
I'm not feeling well.

19:02.830 --> 19:03.550
You're not feeling well?

19:03.590 --> 19:04.680
What's wrong?

19:04.090 --> 19:05.360
♫The person I trust♫

19:05.070 --> 19:05.790
It's so cold here.

19:05.730 --> 19:06.840
♫You are most deserving♫

19:05.830 --> 19:07.010
We can't just sit here.

19:07.100 --> 19:07.990
Lu Yan.

19:07.540 --> 19:10.460
♫Of good things♫

19:08.910 --> 19:09.790
Lu Yan.

19:10.010 --> 19:10.910
I'm here.

19:10.950 --> 19:11.790
I'm here.

19:11.740 --> 19:13.430
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

19:11.830 --> 19:12.460
Lu Yan.

19:14.360 --> 19:15.790
Do you have your ID card with you?

19:14.710 --> 19:16.600
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

19:16.250 --> 19:16.760
What?

19:17.930 --> 19:20.350
♫To feel my heartache♫

19:18.030 --> 19:19.620
Do you have your ID card with you?

19:21.210 --> 19:22.600
♫When I no longer have the best♫

19:22.750 --> 19:23.550
Jiang Chengyi.

19:23.400 --> 19:27.480
♫I miss you missing me♫

19:25.120 --> 19:25.970
What are you trying to do?

19:27.390 --> 19:29.680
I-I want to go to a cyber cafe.

19:30.150 --> 19:31.240
Are you drunk?

19:31.340 --> 19:32.230
Are you drunk?

19:32.230 --> 19:32.930
I feel terrible.

19:32.990 --> 19:34.320
You feel terrible, don't you?

19:34.550 --> 19:36.750
I won't feel so terrible if you kiss me.

19:36.780 --> 19:38.490
What if I said I brought my ID card with me?

19:40.870 --> 19:41.640
Really?

20:07.230 --> 20:08.440
I'm going home.

20:12.480 --> 20:13.070
Okay.

20:18.670 --> 20:19.230
Lu Yan.

20:36.150 --> 20:36.690
Good night.

20:42.610 --> 20:43.250
Good night.

22:34.500 --> 22:35.380
Who is it?

22:39.310 --> 22:40.150
Who?

22:43.670 --> 22:44.350
Who?

23:49.350 --> 23:50.740
Is this property management?

23:51.120 --> 23:52.140
Hello, this is the property management.

23:52.170 --> 23:54.200
I'm calling from Building 3, Apartment 603.

23:54.430 --> 23:55.970
There's someone at my door

23:56.120 --> 23:57.630
pressing the doorbell consistently.

23:58.280 --> 23:59.960
Can you get someone to check?

24:00.060 --> 24:01.270
Okay, please wait a moment.

24:01.300 --> 24:01.810
We'll be right there.

24:01.840 --> 24:02.880
Okay, thank you.

24:10.940 --> 24:11.810
Dr. Lu.

24:11.840 --> 24:12.980
We've just checked.

24:13.010 --> 24:14.110
Maybe someone drunk

24:14.110 --> 24:14.870
knocked on the wrong door.

24:14.890 --> 24:16.100
When the security guards patrol tonight,

24:16.150 --> 24:17.560
they'll pay more attention to this building.

24:18.340 --> 24:18.970
Okay.

24:19.150 --> 24:19.990
Thank you.

24:20.110 --> 24:21.760
Lock the door when you sleep.

24:21.830 --> 24:22.310
Call us

24:22.310 --> 24:23.350
if anything happens.

24:23.650 --> 24:24.410
Thank you.

24:24.440 --> 24:25.240
Okay.

24:45.800 --> 24:53.670
[Huiting Complex]

26:15.230 --> 26:16.300
Isn't this Lu's bike?

26:16.300 --> 26:17.550
Uncle Yue, what happened?

26:17.570 --> 26:18.330
I don't know.

26:18.360 --> 26:18.990
Yue,

26:19.030 --> 26:20.070
what kind of guard are you?

26:20.090 --> 26:21.540
I went out this morning!

26:22.450 --> 26:22.960
You...

26:22.990 --> 26:23.630
What's going on?

26:23.650 --> 26:24.390
Lu.

26:24.420 --> 26:25.550
Look at your bike.

26:25.580 --> 26:26.190
What's going on here?

26:26.190 --> 26:27.050
It's all in pieces.

26:27.070 --> 26:28.290
Call the police now.

26:29.290 --> 26:30.710
How about you call the police now?

26:39.510 --> 26:40.270
Ms. Lu.

26:40.350 --> 26:41.270
Have you noticed

26:41.290 --> 26:42.310
anyone suspicious when you leave

26:42.310 --> 26:43.110
in the mornings lately?

26:44.100 --> 26:45.830
Or did you have any conflicts

26:45.850 --> 26:47.520
with friends or family

26:47.540 --> 26:47.970
recently?

26:48.000 --> 26:48.440
Lu Yan.

26:49.870 --> 26:50.340
You...

26:50.380 --> 26:51.330
Why are you here?

26:51.750 --> 26:52.760
What happened?

26:53.260 --> 26:54.480
When I came out this morning,

26:54.500 --> 26:56.750
I found my bike dismantled.

26:57.150 --> 26:57.870
Ms. Lu.

26:57.900 --> 26:59.140
This is...

26:59.510 --> 27:00.910
He is...

27:02.270 --> 27:04.190
He's a friend from college.

27:05.520 --> 27:06.310
Alright, Ms. Lu.

27:06.350 --> 27:07.150
We understand

27:07.170 --> 27:08.050
the situation now.

27:08.180 --> 27:08.790
Make sure to

27:08.790 --> 27:09.630
stay safe these days,

27:09.650 --> 27:10.290
alright?

27:10.550 --> 27:11.580
Stay contactable.

27:11.610 --> 27:12.970
We'll contact you if there's any news.

27:13.150 --> 27:13.680
Okay.

27:14.050 --> 27:14.510
Thank you.

27:14.510 --> 27:14.990
Thank you.

27:17.240 --> 27:18.030
You...

27:18.290 --> 27:19.740
Are you here for me?

27:21.400 --> 27:22.390
Well,

27:22.410 --> 27:24.260
isn't my dad having the surgery today?

27:24.710 --> 27:26.070
I brought you some breakfast.

27:27.360 --> 27:28.350
Let's go together.

27:30.790 --> 27:31.880
Let's go.

27:32.310 --> 27:34.070
Uncle still needs to do some pre-surgery preparations.

27:37.310 --> 27:38.470
Have you...

27:38.960 --> 27:40.000
offended anyone recently?

27:43.070 --> 27:44.030
I don't think so.

27:54.080 --> 27:55.270
So you're saying that last night,

27:55.310 --> 27:56.820
someone knocked on your door in the middle of the night,

27:56.990 --> 27:58.270
and tried looking inside from the peephole?

27:58.290 --> 27:58.890
Right?

28:01.790 --> 28:03.030
Did he say anything?

28:03.550 --> 28:04.290
No.

28:05.550 --> 28:06.990
Do you remember his face?

28:10.740 --> 28:12.310
I couldn't see his face clearly.

28:12.500 --> 28:13.630
But I called

28:13.650 --> 28:14.370
property management then.

28:15.090 --> 28:16.540
They didn't find anything either.

28:17.280 --> 28:18.790
If this happens again

28:19.220 --> 28:20.050
and you feel it's dangerous,

28:20.270 --> 28:20.990
call the police first.

28:23.480 --> 28:24.570
Not to that extent at least.

28:25.200 --> 28:26.360
I am guessing...

28:26.980 --> 28:28.730
someone's pranking me.

28:31.280 --> 28:31.910
Alright.

28:31.930 --> 28:33.120
Don't worry too much.

28:35.590 --> 28:36.590
You can call me too.

28:48.670 --> 28:49.370
Okay.

29:10.530 --> 29:13.640
[Today's operation]

29:11.500 --> 29:12.860
Don't be nervous.

29:13.920 --> 29:14.590
There's

29:14.610 --> 29:16.380
Dr. Han and Dr. Lu with you.

29:18.020 --> 29:19.260
Just take it as a nap.

29:19.280 --> 29:20.620
You'll be okay once you wake up.

29:20.770 --> 29:22.600
[Today's operation]

29:22.700 --> 29:25.350
[Coats]

29:23.510 --> 29:24.580
We'll wait for you.

29:24.610 --> 29:25.450
Be careful.

29:28.890 --> 29:30.300
Thank you, Dr. Lu.

29:30.320 --> 29:31.620
Auntie, don't worry.

29:52.710 --> 29:53.470
Uncle.

29:53.750 --> 29:54.680
Relax.

29:54.750 --> 29:55.630
I'll be giving you

29:55.650 --> 29:56.500
some calming medicine.

29:56.520 --> 29:57.580
It won't hurt.

29:59.450 --> 30:01.200
Inject 1mg of Midazolam.

30:09.200 --> 30:10.040
Injection complete.

30:22.020 --> 30:22.600
Okay.

30:24.990 --> 30:26.020
Completed tripartite verification?

30:26.130 --> 30:27.210
Yes, it's completed. No errors.

30:28.470 --> 30:29.190
Jiang.

30:29.920 --> 30:30.850
I'm here.

30:31.600 --> 30:33.080
Don't be nervous. Relax.

30:33.530 --> 30:34.340
Just sleep.

30:34.870 --> 30:35.960
You'll be fine after a sleep.

30:38.480 --> 30:39.240
Let's begin.

30:40.030 --> 30:40.720
Uncle.

30:40.750 --> 30:42.330
Get ready to sleep.

30:42.430 --> 30:43.310
After the surgery,

30:43.350 --> 30:44.430
I'll call your name.

30:44.540 --> 30:46.480
Remember to open your eyes and take a deep breath.

30:48.870 --> 30:50.700
Sufentanil, 20mg.

30:56.380 --> 30:57.220
Injection complete.

30:57.270 --> 30:58.800
Propofol, 150 mg.

31:01.640 --> 31:02.380
Injection complete.

31:02.470 --> 31:04.360
Rocuronium, 50mg.

31:07.070 --> 31:07.980
Injection complete.

31:42.790 --> 31:43.570
Dr. Han.

31:43.910 --> 31:45.130
We can set him into position.

31:46.920 --> 31:48.890
One, two, three.

32:15.370 --> 32:20.250
[Operating Room]

32:28.810 --> 32:29.330
Have a seat.

32:29.420 --> 32:29.900
It's okay.

32:30.030 --> 32:30.790
Sit down.

32:30.830 --> 32:32.240
What's taking them so long?

32:32.360 --> 32:32.910
Have a seat.

32:32.910 --> 32:33.590
I'll get you some water.

32:43.400 --> 32:44.140
Here.

32:45.990 --> 32:47.370
Why is it so long?

32:47.750 --> 32:48.830
Is something wrong?

32:48.870 --> 32:49.550
Nothing's wrong.

32:50.160 --> 32:50.940
Don't worry.

33:20.220 --> 33:21.020
Send it for freezing.

33:23.200 --> 33:25.150
We'll attend to the wound while waiting for the pathology results.

33:25.170 --> 33:25.920
Okay.

33:26.000 --> 33:26.610
Lu Yan.

33:27.170 --> 33:28.200
How is his blood pressure?

33:28.330 --> 33:29.310
Everything is normal.

33:31.380 --> 33:32.190
Needle holder.

33:41.940 --> 33:42.870
Dr. Han.

33:44.280 --> 33:45.860
The surgery was a success.

33:46.090 --> 33:48.160
Dr. Lu controlled his blood pressure

33:48.180 --> 33:48.970
very well.

33:50.570 --> 33:51.360
Your dad is fine.

33:51.390 --> 33:52.030
He's fine. Don't worry.

33:52.050 --> 33:52.980
He's fine now, right?

33:53.850 --> 33:55.410
Thank you, Dr. Han.

33:55.750 --> 33:56.840
Your dad is now fine.

33:56.870 --> 33:57.230
Right?

33:57.270 --> 33:57.830
You're welcome.

33:58.170 --> 33:59.390
It's what we're supposed to do.

33:59.720 --> 34:00.830
Jiang is currently waking up

34:00.850 --> 34:01.720
from the anesthesia.

34:01.910 --> 34:03.350
He will be sent out soon.

34:04.180 --> 34:05.230
Thank you, Dr. Han.

34:05.470 --> 34:06.290
Don't worry.

34:20.800 --> 34:21.670
Uncle.

34:23.020 --> 34:23.800
Uncle.

34:25.370 --> 34:26.230
It's time to wake up.

34:34.840 --> 34:36.190
Don't rush into speaking.

34:36.320 --> 34:37.949
Your throat might hurt for a few days.

34:37.989 --> 34:39.360
It's considered normal.

34:39.590 --> 34:40.659
You'll be fine in a few days.

34:43.670 --> 34:44.760
Dr. Lu.

34:43.719 --> 34:48.159
[Bed 3]

34:46.840 --> 34:47.929
Thank you.

34:48.659 --> 34:49.370
Auntie.

34:49.409 --> 34:50.600
This is what we're supposed to do.

34:50.909 --> 34:51.840
We also did

34:51.870 --> 34:53.610
a pathological examination on the teratoma.

34:53.790 --> 34:54.780
It is benign.

34:55.179 --> 34:55.909
We just have to wait

34:55.949 --> 34:57.120
for the final results.

34:57.650 --> 34:58.420
Okay.

34:58.910 --> 35:00.130
Sorry for troubling you.

35:00.330 --> 35:01.070
Don't worry anymore.

35:01.100 --> 35:01.950
Get Uncle

35:03.030 --> 35:03.790
to rest up more.

35:03.820 --> 35:04.390
Okay.

35:08.830 --> 35:09.510
Thank you.

35:20.380 --> 35:21.230
I'll leave now.

35:21.350 --> 35:22.030
Okay.

35:22.050 --> 35:23.040
I'll leave you to it.

35:28.690 --> 35:29.560
Jiang.

35:38.460 --> 35:41.940
[Access Point]

35:41.140 --> 35:42.110
Wrong input.

35:42.140 --> 35:43.540
Invalid number.

36:09.640 --> 36:10.540
Thank you.

36:11.520 --> 36:12.620
Thank you for today.

36:16.610 --> 36:18.050
I promised you, didn't I?

36:18.080 --> 36:19.260
Besides,

36:20.320 --> 36:21.640
this is what I should do.

36:25.380 --> 36:26.810
You haven't changed at all.

36:27.960 --> 36:29.020
You're just like before.

36:32.470 --> 36:34.470
I still remember you said

36:34.840 --> 36:36.590
you wanted to be

36:36.960 --> 36:38.030
an excellent doctor.

36:39.150 --> 36:40.010
You've done it.

36:42.530 --> 36:43.540
You too.

36:43.880 --> 36:45.570
You became

36:46.300 --> 36:47.710
a very good policeman.

36:52.190 --> 36:53.160
Do you know why I

36:53.190 --> 36:54.190
became a police officer then?

36:55.420 --> 36:56.360
Of course I knew.

36:56.430 --> 36:57.390
It's because of

36:57.980 --> 36:58.670
your dad.

36:59.400 --> 37:00.390
There was some influence

37:00.390 --> 37:01.230
from my dad.

37:02.570 --> 37:03.840
But...

37:06.350 --> 37:07.880
the most fundamental reason

37:09.490 --> 37:10.390
is actually you.

37:26.900 --> 37:29.560
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

37:30.330 --> 37:33.350
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

37:31.420 --> 37:33.030
What else do you want to do

37:33.050 --> 37:33.890
after you've become a policeman?

37:34.510 --> 37:36.890
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

37:37.030 --> 37:37.830
Catch the bad guys.

37:37.510 --> 37:40.470
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

37:38.490 --> 37:39.980
I'll catch all of them.

37:41.300 --> 37:42.600
I hope

37:41.850 --> 37:44.600
♫I long to hold your hands and weave beautiful dreams for you♫

